# FBA Backend

Generated by `fbago init [[ .Module ]]`.

## Layout

- `cmd/api`: HTTP entrypoint.
- `internal/app`: project-owned business modules. Put admin, dict, order, payment, and other editable business code here.
- `.env`: local defaults. Real system environment variables override this file.

## Commands

```bash
make tidy
make test
make build
make run
```
